===Noun===
'''gangue'''

#(''Mining'') The [[earthy]] [[waste]] substances occuring in [[metallic]] [[ore]].
#:'''Quotations'''
#:*'''1995''': Thus the percentage recovery of metal from the ore was much higher than in the primitive process where the semi-vitrified gangue and half-smelted ore are typically rich in prills of copper and copper minerals. &mdash; Paul T. Craddock, ''Early Metal Mining and Production'', page 147.

